  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Call of Duty: Modern Warfare - Mobilized is the third Call of Duty video game developed for the Nintendo DS. It features the same first-person shooter gameplay found in its predecessors, and also includes new weapons and vehicles, new mini-games, such as cracking computer terminals, and taking control of UAV Recon Drones and an AC-130 gunship.",
